		"name": "Spring Boot CRUD - Product API",
		"description": "Complete Postman collection for the Spring Boot CRUD REST API with JPA Repository.\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:8080\n\nEndpoints covered:\n- Create Product (POST)\n- Get All Products (GET)\n- Get Product by ID (GET)\n- Update Product (PUT)\n- Delete Product (DELETE)\n- Filter by Category (GET)\n- Search by Name (GET)\n- Filter by Price Range (GET)",
